Enable AutoSuggestion/AutoComplete Use This Command:
Find AwsCompleter Using:which aws_completer->/usr/bin/aws_completer
Then Use Directory Value Here:complete -C '/usr/bin/aws_completer' aws
=====================================================================================Step:04:Credential Order===================================================================
1.Command Line Option->2.Environmental Variables[AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID,AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY]->3.Credential File[~/.aws/credentials]->4.Configuration File[~/.aws/config]->
5.Instance ProfileCredentials.

1.Command Line Option->2.Environmental Variables
Select Above Instance->Instance Settings->Attach/Replace IAM Role->Select No Role[Detach].
GoTo IAM->Add user->User name[AwsCliUser]->Access type[Programmatic access]->Set permissions for User->Attach existing policies directly[AmazonEC2ReadOnlyAccess]->Create User
Get Access Key Id[xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx] & Secret AccessKeyId[xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx] For AwsCliUser.
Do aws ec2 describe-instances.--No output will be Returned.
    export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
    export AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
Do aws ec2 describe-instances.--output will be Returned.
    unset AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID
    unset AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
3.Credential File[~/.aws/credentials]->4.Configuration File[~/.aws/config]    
Do aws configure:
AWS Access Key ID [None]: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
AWS Secret Access Key [None]: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
Default region name [ap-southeast-1]: ap-southeast-1
Default output format [None]:
Do aws ec2 describe-instances.--output will be Returned.
Credential File[~/.aws/credentials] Will Take Precedence Over Config File[~/.aws/config]
Remove 2 File: rm ~/.aws/credentials ~/.aws/config & Delete User/Group/Role For AwsCliUser[Detach policy Form User In Permissions Tab,Make inactive Then Delete Access keys 
In Security Credentials Tab].

5.Instance ProfileCredentials.
Select Above Instance->Instance Settings->Attach/Replace IAM Role->Select AdministratorAccessForEc2ServiceRole[Attach].
Do aws configure->AWS Access Key ID [None]:->AWS Secret Access Key [None]:->Default region name [None]: ap-southeast-1->Default output format [None]:
Do aws ec2 describe-instances.--output will be Returned.